          <h1>Welcome to Me In Time</h1>
          <p>Thanks for stopping by. Whether you’re here because you’re struggling, curious about therapy or coaching, or just thinking things through — I hope this space feels calm, grounded, and genuinely welcoming. Me In Time is about creating room for reflection, growth, and real connection. No pressure. No judgement. Just time for you, as you are.</p>
